    "name": "Serpent's Gaze",
    "steam_appid": 3069050,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《<strong>Serpent’s Gaze</strong>》是一款支持<strong>1-4</strong>人合作的第三人称动作游戏。在一片古老荒漠中，你要直面强大的敌人以及无情的头目，逐步揭开尘封的秘密。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>-</strong> <strong>魂系战斗，融合类ROGUE元素</strong> <strong>-</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3069050/extras/0360dbdc2827fe97014f16b2a29517d5.poster.avif?t=1772022681\" width=620 height=268 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3069050/extras/0360dbdc2827fe97014f16b2a29517d5.webm?t=1772022681\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3069050/extras/0360dbdc2827fe97014f16b2a29517d5.mp4?t=1772022681\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >选择你最喜爱的武器，在惨烈且充满策略的战斗中迎战强敌，还有丰富多样的升级强化助你成功。在精心打造的关卡中杀出一条血路，直面各色头目——无论多少次，都不要放弃。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>- 可以组队协作，也可以独自迎接挑战</strong> <strong>-</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3069050/extras/3e8f54b1192b2c69d527d2e6a70cf6e1.poster.avif?t=1772022681\" width=620 height=268 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3069050/extras/3e8f54b1192b2c69d527d2e6a70cf6e1.webm?t=1772022681\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3069050/extras/3e8f54b1192b2c69d527d2e6a70cf6e1.mp4?t=1772022681\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >最多可支持4人协作，你可以和同伴并肩克服这个世界的重重考验，亦可独自按自己的步调前行。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>- 收集祝福，选择战斗风格</strong> <strong>-</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3069050/extras/8dd0323a821a46355bc85f057983c004.poster.avif?t=1772022681\" width=620 height=268 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3069050/extras/8dd0323a821a46355bc85f057983c004.webm?t=1772022681\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3069050/extras/8dd0323a821a46355bc85f057983c004.mp4?t=1772022681\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在你过关斩将的过程中，你会获得种种提升——陌生神明的祝福、庇护者的馈赠，还有在朝圣路上能帮到你的奇异遗宝。谨慎抉择，探索无尽的策略与可能。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>- 遭到诸神诅咒，迎接全新的挑战</strong> <strong>-</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3069050/extras/305fa553f85dabde9fac3b727bfb054a.poster.avif?t=1772022681\" width=620 height=268 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3069050/extras/305fa553f85dabde9fac3b727bfb054a.webm?t=1772022681\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3069050/extras/305fa553f85dabde9fac3b727bfb054a.mp4?t=1772022681\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >诅咒系统为每一次冒险带来随机变数——从被小头目追杀到遭遇环境陷阱，这一切让你的下一次新旅程始终充满新鲜与挑战。 <br>警觉系统带来进一步挑战，使每一次成功的征途都愈发艰难。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>- 探索古老沙漠以及其中埋藏的秘密</strong> <strong>-</strong> </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3069050/extras/d9e585637d1ae316d991bce7c243d8b4.poster.avif?t=1772022681\" width=620 height=268 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3069050/extras/d9e585637d1ae316d991bce7c243d8b4.webm?t=1772022681\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3069050/extras/d9e585637d1ae316d991bce7c243d8b4.mp4?t=1772022681\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在各大势力盘踞的险恶环境中杀出一条血路。沙漠与废墟属于游牧民马金，那座有大圣堂的城市里则住着傲慢的阿塔埃什。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>- 揭示创造者的真正意图</strong> <strong>-</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3069050/extras/eb0b4c2f91bdaae8a47a9b650ca61b1d.poster.avif?t=1772022681\" width=620 height=268 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3069050/extras/eb0b4c2f91bdaae8a47a9b650ca61b1d.webm?t=1772022681\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3069050/extras/eb0b4c2f91bdaae8a47a9b650ca61b1d.mp4?t=1772022681\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你是枯萎树神玉兰孕育的后裔，只为讨伐现今统治此地的诸神与篡位者。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >欲让荒漠再度绽放生机，唯有以暴制暴。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"></p>",
